_sText:
This is my first good map.
You are in an old, desolate warehouse.
There are two bomb places.
One is evident, the other is hidden.
There is a confidential workroom also.
Achievement is this space only by an air shaft.

Result:
Though it is not so creepy, indeed, nevertheless, the map gives very much pleasure, because there many ways is the opposing team to defeat.
Unfortunately, this map is not well suitable for Bots.

A lot of fun!

************

Idea's: Marco Leuthner
